    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289720/extras/dd6e7f4391915770823a4cf55db79f5d.poster.avif?t=1770896091\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289720/extras/dd6e7f4391915770823a4cf55db79f5d.webm?t=1770896091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289720/extras/dd6e7f4391915770823a4cf55db79f5d.mp4?t=1770896091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《涅亚》是一款第一人称指向点击冒险游戏。其背景设定在偏远且几乎废弃的群岛上，这些岛屿被一系列复杂的传送门机械所分隔，两种奇异的文化曾在这留下自己独特的痕迹。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从一个奇怪的梦中醒来后，你发现自己被传送到了一个名为奥卢杰的地方。你遇到了瓦米尔，他把你送往涅亚，并希望你在那一切顺利。瓦米尔交给你一项紧急任务，而你将在探索中发现其背后的原因。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一个错误必须被纠正。一个文明要复仇。一个秘密将被揭开。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你到达涅亚时，手忙脚乱的瓦米尔只给了你少量关于如何执行任务的知识。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >事情没有按计划发展。为了返回奥卢杰并找到瓦米尔，你必须探索涅亚——将分散在奇特风景中的机械装置、生锈的操纵杆和蓝色的等离子传送门系统联系在一起，了解曾经塑造涅亚的文明。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >并非一切都如你所见，当你进一步深入涅亚的古老核心时，你的发现将引领你揭开地球命运背后的真相……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289720/extras/d6604d6da4de344abbed4f21a03b1998.poster.avif?t=1770896091\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289720/extras/d6604d6da4de344abbed4f21a03b1998.webm?t=1770896091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289720/extras/d6604d6da4de344abbed4f21a03b1998.mp4?t=1770896091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特性</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精美的预渲染图形，具有高度的丰富性和真实感。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >营造氛围的原创音轨。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >引人入胜的音效，让你深入了解周围的世界。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >易于使用的2D风格点击界面，各种光标选项能让你始终知道在与什么进行互动。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >四种移动过渡选项：关/快速/中等/休闲，适应每个人的游戏风格。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快速旅行模式，让你能跳过某些场景，更快地穿过这个世界，更高效地到达目的地。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>观察、记录、思考</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《涅亚》反映了类似我们自己社会中的情况，比如什么是真实的，什么是虚假的，以及质疑自己的信仰的能力。通过环境叙事，玩家能享受数小时的非线性游戏，使用认真观察、视觉关联、自行记录、使用库存物品等手段解开谜题，同时也能沉浸在丰富的故事和环境驱动的游戏中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>让涅亚成为你命中注定要探索的世界……</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289720/extras/d99e4def30827082d5b585a46c4b70fc.poster.avif?t=1770896091\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289720/extras/d99e4def30827082d5b585a46c4b70fc.webm?t=1770896091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289720/extras/d99e4def30827082d5b585a46c4b70fc.mp4?t=1770896091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
